{"tid":623985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放蛇搭Uber　警被指沒戴安全帶","createTime":"2018-04-10T12:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T07:46:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce692d00e9b8696a2664d8b42ce73d3a6a5443e","tid":623985,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20356976?_ga=2.41141282.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20356976%3F_ga%3D2.41141282.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=Ukj8UmeDpgCjf6vvV5WuSgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=f6c26bf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20356976%3F_ga%3D2.41141282.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=2899b64b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20356976?_ga=2.41141282.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n放蛇搭Uber　警被指沒戴安全帶<br />\n<br />\n5.8K<br />\n法庭<br />\n <br />\n九龍城法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方去年採取行動，派員放蛇乘搭Uber，事後拘捕多個Uber司機，其中23人被控「駕駛汽車以作出租或取酬載客用途」罪，法庭於昨天起分批處理各案件。控方昨讀出其中一名放蛇男警的書面供詞，稱放蛇警乘車期間遭交通警截停，指他沒佩戴安全帶，放蛇警辯稱是汽車被截停後才解安全帶，終獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n昨在九龍城裁判法院處理的案件涉及被告翁浩祥（39歲）及葉惠明（32歲），均被指在去年4月28日非法載客取酬，2人不認罪。控方針對2人的案件完成舉證，裁判官裁定2人表證成立，案件押後至5月28日作結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC3412-3/17<br />\n■記者黃幗慧"},{"pid":"f7eac9899bb9a7a9f1a022d69098a930cff536cc","tid":623985,"uid":33729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3db8818afbebd043c2a96cfe042d13adae1e16c","tid":623985,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"反咬 good job"},{"pid":"fbd78f0a2b877608d97dd390c496def6a7177e91",